Package eu.datacrop.maize.model_repository.api.error

Class ErrorMessage

java.lang.Object
eu.datacrop.maize.model_repository.api.error.ErrorMessage
public class ErrorMessage extends Object
This class is a data transfer object representing an Error Message. Used in HTTP responses that do not correspond to successful responses (codes 200-299).
Since:
version 0.3.0
Author:
Angela-Maria Despotopoulou [Athens, Greece]
